      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This lot of the papers of Edward E. Younger consists of ca.
         425 items (3 Hollinger boxes, ca. 1.3 linear shelf feet),
         1942-1979, relating to Younger's naval services and his tenure
         as professor of American History and chairman of the
         department at the University of Virginia. The collection is
         divided into four series: Correspondence, Topical Files,
         Student Papers, and Non-student Papers.</p>
      </scopecontent>
